{"comments":"Partition Matroid for Render Tier Constraints\n\nA partition matroid is defined by:\n- A partition of the ground set E = P₁ ∪ P₂ ∪ ... ∪ Pₘ\n- Cardinality bounds k₁, k₂, ..., kₘ for each partition\n- A set S is independent iff |S ∩ Pᵢ| ≤ kᵢ for all i\n\n## Render Tier Application\n\nFor adaptive rendering, we partition regions into three tiers:\n- **Foveal** (P₁): High-priority gaze-centered regions, k₁ = 8\n- **Peripheral** (P₂): Medium-priority context regions, k₂ = 16\n- **Background** (P₃): Low-priority ambient regions, k₃ = 32\n\nTotal budget: 56 regions per frame\n\nThis partition reflects the human visual system: highest quality where\nthe user is looking (fovea), moderate quality in peripheral vision,\nand minimum quality in the background.\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Render","Online","Matroid","Partition"],"TierBounds"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[177,67],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Render/Online/Matroid/Partition.purs","start":[177,32]},"title":"TieredPartitionMatroid"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Render","Online","Matroid","Partition"],"TieredPartitionMatroid"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[179,70],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Render/Online/Matroid/Partition.purs","start":[179,1]},"title":"eqTieredPartitionMatroid"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Render","Online","Matroid","Partition"],"TieredPartitionMatroid"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[183,52],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Render/Online/Matroid/Partition.purs","start":[181,1]},"title":"showTieredPartitionMatroid"},{"comments":"Matroid instance for region selection\n\nA set of selections is independent iff:\n- foveal count ≤ foveal bound\n- peripheral count ≤ peripheral bound\n- background count ≤ background bound\n","info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Render","Online","Matroid","Class"],"Matroid"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Render","Online","Matroid","Partition"],"TieredPartitionMatroid"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Render","Online","Core"],"RegionSelection"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[209,22],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Render/Online/Matroid/Partition.purs","start":[195,1]},"title":"matroidTieredPartition"}],"comments":"Partition matroid over render tiers\n\nThe ground set is partitioned into three tiers based on render priority.\nA selection is independent (feasible) if the count from each tier does\nnot exceed the tier's bound.\n\nThis encodes the constraint: \"At most k₁ foveal, k₂ peripheral, k₃ background\"\n","info":{"dataDeclType":"newtype","declType":"data","roles":[],"typeArguments":[]},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[177,67],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Render/Online/Matroid/Partition.purs","start":[177,1]},"title":"TieredPartitionMatroid"},{"children":[],"comments":"Construct a tiered partition matroid with bounds\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Render","Online","Matroid","Partition"],"TierBounds"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Render","Online","Matroid","Partition"],"TieredPartitionMatroid"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[186,65],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Render/Online/Matroid/Partition.purs","start":[186,1]},"title":"mkTieredPartitionMatroid"},{"children":[],"comments":"Default tier bounds from ML expert analysis\n\n- Foveal: 8 (high quality, ~14% of budget)\n- Peripheral: 16 (medium quality, ~29% of budget)  \n- Background: 32 (low quality, ~57% of budget)\n\nTotal: 56 regions per frame\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Render","Online","Matroid","Partition"],"TierBounds"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[117,32],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Render/Online/Matroid/Partition.purs","start":[117,1]},"title":"defaultTierBounds"},{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Record"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["fovealCount",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Int"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["peripheralCount",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Int"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["backgroundCount",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Int"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"tag":"REmpty"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[133,4],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Render/Online/Matroid/Partition.purs","start":[129,20]},"title":"TierCounts"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Render","Online","Matroid","Partition"],"TierCounts"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[135,46],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Render/Online/Matroid/P